The paper is about machine reading comprehension for question answering, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques and multi-task learning, which are common in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with attention mechanisms, which are relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which are relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
